data.description: CONTRACTS ARE NOW BEING ACCEPTED! Welcome to America's #1 Home Builder, D. R. Horton in the Arbors of Farms at New Kent Neighborhood! The Penwell home features a large great room that is excellent for entertaining. The kitchen comes nicely appointed with beautiful Stone Gray cabinets, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash and large walk-in pantry! Upstairs is perfect for your family featuring generously sized bedrooms all with walk-in closets. The flex space is perfect for office, craft room or formal dining. The full-finished basement featuring a comfortable recreation room, bedroom and full bathroom is a great space for game room, in-law suite, or home theatre. This home will also come with a 14x12 deck thats perfect for entertaining outdoors. Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, tankless water heater, and our Smart Home package will be included! Close to Viniterra Winery!
